Marketplace images management commands.

USAGE:
  scw marketplace image <command>

AVAILABLE COMMANDS:
  get         Get a specific marketplace image
  list        List marketplace images

FLAGS:
  -h, --help                help for image
      --list-sub-commands   List all subcommands

GLOBAL FLAGS:
  -c, --config string    The path to the config file
  -D, --debug            Enable debug mode
  -o, --output string    Output format: json or human, see 'scw help output' for more info (default "human")
  -p, --profile string   The config profile to use

Use "scw marketplace image [command] --help" for more information about a command.
